<view class="page"><view class="hero-card"><view class="hero-title">花园成长规则</view><view class="hero-subtitle">照料越用心，花朵成长越快</view></view><view class="card"><view class="section-title">动作得分</view><view class="score-grid"><view class="score-item"><view class="score-icon">💧</view><view class="score-name">浇水</view><view class="score-value">+1</view></view><view class="score-item"><view class="score-icon">🧪</view><view class="score-name">施肥</view><view class="score-value">+2</view></view><view class="score-item"><view class="score-icon">🌿</view><view class="score-name">除草</view><view class="score-value">+1</view></view></view></view><view class="card"><view class="section-title">阶段成长</view><view class="timeline"><view class="timeline-row"><view class="dot"></view><view class="line"></view><view class="dot"></view><view class="line"></view><view class="dot"></view></view><view class="timeline-labels"><view class="timeline-label">种子 0分</view><view class="timeline-label">幼苗 9分</view><view class="timeline-label">开花 18分</view></view></view><view class="highlight">每达到 9 分，花朵成长到下一阶段</view></view><view class="card"><view class="section-title">详细说明</view><view class="rule-item"><text class="rule-index">1.</text><text class="rule-text">每位用户都会拥有自己的花园，花园内默认有多种花可照料。</text></view><view class="rule-item"><text class="rule-index">2.</text><text class="rule-text">每种养护动作每天有次数限制，达到上限后当日不可重复操作。</text></view><view class="rule-item"><text class="rule-index">3.</text><text class="rule-text">可在首页切换当前照料的花，养护分值仅对当前选中的花生效。</text></view><view class="rule-item"><text class="rule-index">4.</text><text class="rule-text">阶段成长顺序为：种子 - 幼苗 - 开花，照料记录会体现在成长日志。</text></view></view><view class="tip-card">小提示：优先施肥可以更快进入下一阶段。</view></view>